..TEXT:
Like Christian going up the hill Difficulty in
Bunyan, ^Pilgrim's Progress~: "I looked then after Christian to
see him go up the hill, where I perceived he fell from running to
going, and from going to clambering upon his hands and knees,
because of the steepness of the place."
